<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA516_06_IH_0007</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema516_06_ih.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema516_06.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema516_06_ih_0007">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="7" class="is_star" lang="y">단위를 잘못 사용한 것을 찾아 기호를 쓰고, 단위를 옳게 고쳐 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="img_area">
          <div class="boolean_wrap justify_center">
            <div>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">
                <p class="flex align_center gap_8"><i class="num_sign">ㄱ</i> 강원특별자치도의 넓이는 약 16830 ㎢입니다.</p>
              </button>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="false">
                <p class="flex align_center gap_8"><i class="num_sign">ㄴ</i> 색종이의 넓이는 225 ㎠입니다.</p>
              </button>
              <button type="button" data-answer-single="true">
                <p class="flex align_center gap_8"><i class="num_sign">ㄷ</i> 축구장의 넓이는 약 7140 ㎢입니다.</p>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p lang="y" class="text_desc">(출처: 공공데이터포털, 2024)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex align_center justify_center mt_10">
          <span class="label_gray" lang="y">옳게 고치기</span>
          <div class="input_wrap_underline">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">축구장의 넓이는 약 7140 ㎡입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">강원특별자치도의 넓이를 나타낼 때에는 ㎢, 색종이의 넓이를 나타낼 때에는 ㎠, 축구장의 넓이를 나타낼 때에는 ㎡가 알맞습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit" data-submit="true">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
